OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's two largest parties
OL,7,Fare divided over UK Government plans
OL,8,Fto boost the region's defence sector
OL,9,Fwith #50 million.
OL,11,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson said First
OL,12,FMinister Michelle O'Neill had chosen
OL,13,F"ideological grandstanding" over the
OL,14,Finvestment deal, which Sinn Fein MP
OL,15,FChris Hazzard described as indicative
OL,16,Fof the UK Government's "immoral
OL,17,Fpolitical choice to supercharge the
OL,18,Fbuilding of weapons of war".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@[O]xD@XOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
