FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,FDefence minister Luke Pollard visited
OL,7,FBelfast on Wednesday with Northern
OL,8,FIreland Office minister Matthew
OL,9,FPatrick to meet representatives from
OL,10,Flocal industry and research, to launch
OL,11,Fthe Northern Ireland Defence Growth
OL,12,FDeal.
OL,14,FOfficials said the deal ` part of the
OL,15,FUK Government's Defence Industrial
OL,16,FStrategy, will create a targeted
OL,17,Fprogramme to help small and medium-
OL,18,Fsized enterprises (SMEs) and start-ups
OL,19,Fin Northern Ireland by making it
OL,20,Feasier for them to enter the defence
OL,21,Fsupply chain.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,FIt will also focus on supporting SMEs
OL,7,Fin developing technology that can be
OL,8,Fused for military and civilian
OL,9,Fpurposes, ensuring new technologies
OL,10,Fbenefit UK national security and the
OL,11,Fwider economy.
OL,13,FAlongside the #50 million investment,
OL,14,Fthe UK Government has said it will
OL,15,Fprovide additional funding for a
OL,16,Fskills initiative in Northern Ireland.
OL,18,FMr Pollard said the region "plays a
OL,19,Fpivotal role in keeping the UK and our
OL,20,Fallies safe".
OL,26,@zD@\OU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,F"In Belfast we build missiles that
OL,7,Ftake down Iranian drones threatening
OL,8,Four bases and allies in the Middle
OL,9,FEast," he said.
OL,11,F"Belfast also builds the air defence
OL,12,Fsystems that keep Ukraine in the fight
OL,13,Fagainst Putin's illegal war."
OL,15,FThe launch on Wednesday was attended
OL,16,Fby DUP deputy First Minister Emma
OL,17,FLittle-Pengelly but not Ms O'Neill or
OL,18,FEconomy Minister Caoimhe Archibald.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@FO]sD@AOUuD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
