OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,FMr Robinson said the investment is "a
OL,7,Fhugely significant boost for Northern
OL,8,FIreland" and the region has previously
OL,9,Fnot received "its fair share of
OL,10,FMinistry of Defence spending".
OL,12,FHe added: "This funding will support
OL,13,Flocal businesses, strengthen supply
OL,14,Fchains, create highly skilled jobs and
OL,15,Fopen new opportunities for young
OL,16,Fpeople leaving our universities and
OL,17,Fcolleges.
OL,26,@nD@dOUpD@HO]qD@NOUrD@]O]tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,F"Northern Ireland already has over
OL,7,F9,000 people employed in this sector
OL,8,Fand generated around #2.2 billion of
OL,9,Fbusiness last year. This investment
OL,10,Fcan help grow that success even
OL,11,Ffurther."
OL,13,F"It is puerile of Sinn Fein to
OL,14,Fcontinue to oppose opportunities that
OL,15,Fsupport workers and families here.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,F"The First Minister and Economy
OL,7,FMinister ought to be championing
OL,8,Finvestment in Northern Ireland to
OL,9,Fcreate opportunities for local people
OL,10,Fand local business, but instead they
OL,11,Fchoose ideological grandstanding.
OL,13,F"The DUP will continue backing jobs,
OL,14,Findustry and investment.
OL,16,F"This package is about economic
OL,17,Fgrowth, innovation and ensuring
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland gets the support it
OL,19,Fdeserves."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Hazzard said the UK
OL,7,FGovernment is "making a callous and
OL,8,Fimmoral political choice to
OL,9,Fsupercharge the building of weapons of
OL,10,Fwar, while simultaneously ignoring the
OL,11,Fhuge cost-of-living crisis".
OL,13,F"This is also the same British
OL,14,FGovernment that just weeks ago cut
OL,15,Ffunding to our community groups here,
OL,16,Fyet can find #50 million at the drop
OL,17,Fof a hat," he added.
OL,26,@oD@OOUsD@[O]yD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,F"This is yet another slap in the face
OL,7,Fto struggling families who will be
OL,8,Fincredulous and outraged at this
OL,9,Fdecision.
OL,11,F"Once again, communities in the north
OL,12,Fare being harmed by reckless decisions
OL,13,Ftaken in London."
OL,15,FIn Northern Ireland there are 900 jobs
OL,16,Fdirectly supported by more than #271
OL,17,Fmillion of defence industry spending
OL,18,Feach year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
