FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,FWhen asked about a "lack of political
OL,7,Fbuy-in" to the investment deal,
OL,8,FMatthew Patrick said: "I think people
OL,9,Freally welcome this investment.
OL,11,F"It's #50 million investment into the
OL,12,Feconomy of Northern Ireland, helping
OL,13,Fyoung people get good jobs, better
OL,14,Fjobs, helping small businesses expand
OL,15,Fthat supply chain.
OL,26,@nD@TOUoD@GO]pD@WOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
