OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,F"Everyone I speak to is thrilled about
OL,7,Fthis deal, so I think we're working
OL,8,Fpositively across the executive,
OL,9,Facross businesses, to make this a real
OL,10,Fsuccess and I'm really pleased about
OL,11,Fthat."
OL,13,FJoseph Reffitt, Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fdirector at the ADS trade
OL,15,Forganisation, said the Northern Irish
OL,16,Fdefence sector "already makes a
OL,17,Fsubstantial contribution to the local
OL,18,Feconomy, supporting well-paid, highly
OL,19,Fskilled jobs right across the region".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@FO]xD@POU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
