CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776885106
OL,3,C#50m growth deal to help boost NI
OL,4,Cdefence sector
OL,6,F"While the detail will be pivotal, we
OL,7,Fhope this deal will help build on our
OL,8,Fexisting strengths by investing in the
OL,9,Fengineering capability and the
OL,10,Fworkforce we are known for," he said.
